title: Mahler - Symphony No. 9, Lieder - Karajan, BPO, Ludwig
description:
Mahler: Symphony No. 9, Kindertotenlieder, Ruckert Lieder.

Gustav Mahler's Ninth Symphony, Kindertotenlieder, and Ruckert Lieder, recorded by Christa Ludwig (mezzo-soprano), Herbert von Karajan and the Berlin Philharmonic Orchestra. Karajan recorded this symphony twice within two years; this is the earlier analog recording that DG released in 1980. It has been remastered and combined with orchestral lieder recorded in the 1970s for re-release as a double CD.

Please enjoy.
